sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFC as workflow-controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics, 6060/TCP health
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod<br/>(argoexec sidecar)
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over DSP,S3: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    DSP->>K8s: 1. Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8s-->>WFC: 2. Watch event: new Workflow<br/>HTTPS, SA Token
    WFC->>K8s: 3. Create Pod for workflow step<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Note over Pod: argoexec sidecar starts<br/>manages container lifecycle

    Pod->>K8s: 4. Patch Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Pod->>S3: 5. Upload step artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS/S3 credentials
    S3-->>Pod: Artifact stored
    WFC->>K8s: 6. Update Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    Note over WFC,WFC: Repeat steps 3-6 for each workflow step

    Note over Prom,WFC: Flow 2: Metrics Collection

    Prom->>WFC: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/9090, plaintext, no auth

    Note over DSP,S3: Flow 3: Artifact Retrieval (via Argo Server)

    participant AS as argo-server<br/>2746/TCP HTTPS+gRPC

    DSP->>AS: 1. GET /artifacts/{ns}/{name}/..<br/>HTTPS/2746, Bearer/SSO Token
    AS->>S3: 2. Fetch artifact<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS/S3 credentials
    S3-->>AS: Artifact data
    AS-->>DSP: 3. Return artifact<br/>HTTPS/2746
